<p class="c6"><span class="c2">You halt your explanation, surprised by Ledret&rsquo;s interruption. &nbsp;You get the feeling there may be some context you are not aware of. &nbsp;Although, you are aware that frequent rest cycles for the Aggro are part of the resource management plans that have been sweeping Eschaton&hellip; although you were reasonably confident that such had not applied to the Esteemed&rsquo;s personal protectors. &nbsp; Nevertheless, you wait for the Aggro guards to make their ceremonial exit before speaking again.</span></p>
